'''Askira/Uba''' un hukuma pamarun gal diiwal Borno Najeriya hautirde den eɗe ɗer gelle ɗen Askira. Lamba wuro noddirgo go gebbal gal hango wonii 601.<ref>= http://www.nipost.gov.ng/PostCode.aspx | accessdate = 2009-10-20 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20091007011423/http://www.nipost.gov.ng/PostCode.aspx| archivedate= 7 October 2009 | url-status= dead}}</ref> Gotun eɗer saraji Askira uban lassa kanjun woni artuɗun sare hesere waɓɓere yawun ɗun ɗun anɗitoya e ɗer yiyam ɓiyi mishan Amurka eɗeɓe garki ɗen goɗɗun kautuɗu yimɓe ɗarnoɓe ko nonii yawii gabbe yawufuɗɗi anɗituki e suduki goɗaki-goɗaki ɗun inɗe lassa virus inare eɗun fuɗɗi wanguki.<ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=1_XIbBRvD0gC&pg=PA354 |date=9 January 2008 |publisher=SAGE |isbn=978-1-4129-4186-0 |oclc=775277696}}</ref>
E leuru Yulin dundu 2014 woɓɓe ɓe bindiga ɓe ɗun hammoto ɓiɓɓe Boko Haram yari konu e sareji ɗin huyim e dilla gonɗun hukuma pamarun. Askira Uba ɗen ɓe paɗɗi yimɓe jewe nayo e sappo e tate e jewetati. Honoɓe ɓen ɓe gurtoika gada ladde sambisa joɗiɓe ɓe ɗun laggoyi eɓe giɗi walle ki gada ardiɓe e yimɓe ɓe risku.
